:1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T05:06:34.000Z","msg":"周不時見到一團團支那人心口掛唒牌等上樓聽講座<br />\n好多明顯係鄉下佬樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdfde6f7cf79037ac7d397000019aa1140fa0a5","tid":496763,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T05:10:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傻仔先信，可憐好多自以為叻仔既傻仔加入</blockquote><br />\n呢個世界好多傻仔所以呢d騙案永遠唔會停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46906f1903552c2d7c3570529b784426f8de7179","tid":496763,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T05:18:13.000Z","msg":"呃支那人市場大呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9801ea21e53c14f3f696d81af6dc6f7a14b90031","tid":496763,"uid":161305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T05:18:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/160037_28505b63b6b11d32a12bb68fdc273472.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F160037_28505b63b6b11d32a12bb68fdc273472.jpg&h=d68c5cd1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地個maione天使姐做到好撚勁㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/131817_cd0219d31028aba453d9f8047bc72eb0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F131817_cd0219d31028aba453d9f8047bc72eb0.jpeg&h=eadaffa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/131818_f1e82ae9de725ee7efafd50ee26ba680.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F131818_f1e82ae9de725ee7efafd50ee26ba680.jpeg&h=f9ccf386&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4828541a1c9982233e511d3d5e94cf9b23f00fa","tid":496763,"uid":11840,"like":0,